                <h2>Shero’s Journey</h2>
                <p>Shero’s Journey is part of our Stories for Change programming, a series of youth initiatives from the International Storytelling Center. Studies measuring self-confidence show that during pivotal tween years, a girl’s confidence and self-esteem take a major dip, more so than male peers her age, and that the dip is more likely to last into adulthood. This program aims to combat that dip and help girls feel more confident and capable. </p>
